{
  "texts": [
    "The dataset is accompanied by a transcript, which was manually created for 100 speakers.",
    "Bouamor et al. [2018] present MADAR: a manually curated parallel corpus of sentences in Arabic dialects along with English, French and Modern Standard Arabic.",
    "4 Similarly, Riley et al. [2023] create a parallel corpus of English sentences and two dialects each of Portuguese and Chinese with the help of native speakers of these dialects.",
    "Eisenstein et al. [2023] introduce MD-3 a dataset of conversations between speakers playing the game of taboo.",
    "The dataset consists of speech recordings as well as text transcripts."
  ]
}